model.tiles

Interface Evolvable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BuildableTile, CityHall, CommercialTile, HospitalTile, IndustrialTile, PolicestationTile, ResidentialTile, RoadTile

    public interface Evolvable
    An interface for " evolvable " buildings (e.g. residential zones). These buildings can evolve between different construction states.
